cat << EOF
GPSBabel converts waypoint data between about fifty file formats, including
Magellan and Garmin serial, Garmin USB, Mapsource, Mapsend, Streets & Trips,
Delorme, National Geographic, many PDA formats, and many others. It is
endian and word-size safe, includes a GUI, and runs on a variety of operating
systems. It also supports Groundspeak GPX extensions for geocaching.
EOF
